<br>
That's not what I said at all. Raids and exp grouping are two radically different parts of the EQ experience, each should be balanced. It's difficult yes, because raid advantages bleed over into exp groups and vice versa but that does <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>not</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> make it acceptable to balance one <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>against</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> the other.<br>
