A half assed taunt ability<br>
Crits that fire off at normal damage 80% of the time (which other classes now have)<br>
A defensive discipline that I Can use once every 12 weeks<br>
98% reliablility on Proc weapons for help with AGGRO<br>
A horribly painstaking epic for a half assed reward only good for the proc <br>
AA Melee skills that fire off at such low percentages that you may never see them for hours. But if or when they do they only increase DPS by a minute amount <br>
A hitpoint advantage that can be made up for by other means<br>
